---
import HomepageLayout from '../../layouts/HomepageLayout.astro';
---

<HomepageLayout
  title="Tanzania Safari | Experiencia 3D Inmersiva de Vida Salvaje"
  description="Descubre los safaris impresionantes de Tanzania a través de una experiencia 3D inmersiva. Explora el Serengeti, presencia la Gran Migración y planifica tu aventura africana."
  lang="es"
>
  <!-- Video Background -->
  <video class="bg-video" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
    <source src="/media/homepage/safari-bg.mp4" type="video/mp4">
  </video>
  <div class="video-overlay"></div>

  <!-- 3D Background Canvas -->
  <canvas id="webgl-canvas"></canvas>

  <!-- UI Overlay -->
  <main class="content">
    <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
    <section class="panel hero" id="section-hero">
      <div class="glass-box init-anim">
        <h1 class="glow-text">Tanzania Salvaje</h1>
        <p>Desplázate para descubrir la vida salvaje holográfica de la sabana africana.</p>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">
          <div class="mouse"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: Details -->
    <section class="panel details" id="section-details">
      <div class="glass-box left init-anim">
        <h2 class="glow-text">Tanzania Safari</h2>
        <p>A medida que te adentras en las llanuras, la verdadera esencia de África cobra vida. Experimenta los paisajes impresionantes, la increíble vida salvaje y las aventuras inolvidables que te esperan en Tanzania.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2.5: TikTok Safari Grid -->
    <section class="panel tiktok-section" id="section-tiktok">
      <div class="glass-box full-width init-anim">
        <h2 class="glow-text center-text">#Safari #Tanzania Vibraciones</h2>
        <div class="tiktok-grid">
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@nasikiasafaris/video/7521758369460292869" data-video-id="7521758369460292869" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@nasikiasafaris" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@nasikiasafaris?refer=embed">@nasikiasafaris</a> Tanzania Safari <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7521758369460292869?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@zanzibardestination/video/7616776095198694676" data-video-id="7616776095198694676" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@zanzibardestination" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@zanzibardestination?refer=embed">@zanzibardestination</a> Tanzania Safari 2026 <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7616776095198694676?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@allysontaylorrrr/video/7614891117133270303" data-video-id="7614891117133270303" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@allysontaylorrrr" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@allysontaylorrrr?refer=embed">@allysontaylorrrr</a> Africa Travel <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7614891117133270303?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@safarinomara/video/7475299968803147063" data-video-id="7475299968803147063" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@safarinomara" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@safarinomara?refer=embed">@safarinomara</a> Safari Magic <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7475299968803147063?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@tanzanianextlevelsafari/video/7608197353786363157" data-video-id="7608197353786363157" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@tanzanianextlevelsafari" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@tanzanianextlevelsafari?refer=embed">@tanzanianextlevelsafari</a> Tanzania Vibes <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7608197353786363157?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@oa1403/video/7615655140003024150" data-video-id="7615655140003024150" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@oa1403" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@oa1403?refer=embed">@oa1403</a> Serengeti Vibes <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7615655140003024150?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@zanzibardestination/video/7493270037332086071" data-video-id="7493270037332086071" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@zanzibardestination" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@zanzibardestination?refer=embed">@zanzibardestination</a> This is Africa <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7493270037332086071?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@luxtravelbe/video/7246104146288397594" data-video-id="7246104146288397594" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@luxtravelbe" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@luxtravelbe?refer=embed">@luxtravelbe</a> Best Safaris in Tanzania <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7246104146288397594?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="tiktok-card">
            <blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@amberhon__/video/7423323018958507272" data-video-id="7423323018958507272" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 280px;"><section><a target="_blank" title="@amberhon__" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@amberhon__?refer=embed">@amberhon__</a> Safari in Tanzania <a target="_blank" title="♬ original sound" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7423323018958507272?refer=embed">♬ original sound</a></section></blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <script is:inline async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Immersion -->
    <section class="panel immersion" id="section-immersion">
      <div class="glass-box right init-anim">
        <h2 class="glow-text">La Migración</h2>
        <p>La frontera entre la realidad y lo digital se desvanece durante la Gran Migración. Contempla la síntesis definitiva de luz y geometría sagrada.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 4: Pricing -->
    <section class="panel pricing-section" id="section-pricing">
      <div class="glass-box full-width init-anim">
        <h2 class="glow-text center-text">Expediciones Físicas a Tanzania</h2>
        <div class="pricing-cards">
          <div class="price-card">
            <img src="/media/homepage/safari_classic.jpg" alt="Expedición Safari Clásico" class="price-img" loading="lazy">
            <h3>Safari Clásico</h3>
            <p class="price-desc">La aventura esencial. Explora el Serengeti en nuestros vehículos 4x4 totalmente equipados.</p>
            <div class="price">$1,299</div>
            <ul>
              <li>✓ 3 Días de Safari (Serengeti y Ngorongoro)</li>
              <li>✓ Alojamiento en Lodge Estándar</li>
              <li>✓ Todas las Comidas Incluidas</li>
              <li>✓ Traslados de Ida y Vuelta desde Arusha</li>
              <li>✓ Guía Bilingüe Certificado</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="neon-btn">Reservar Viaje</button>
          </div>
          <div class="price-card featured">
            <img src="/media/homepage/safari_balloon.jpg" alt="Safari en Globo Aerostático" class="price-img" loading="lazy">
            <h3>Aventura Serengeti</h3>
            <p class="price-desc">Nuestro paquete más popular. Siente la brisa africana desde las alturas al amanecer.</p>
            <div class="price">$2,499</div>
            <ul>
              <li>★ 5 Días de Safari Extensivo</li>
              <li>★ <strong>Vuelo en Globo Aerostático sobre el Serengeti</strong></li>
              <li>★ Alojamiento Premium en Glamping</li>
              <li>★ Desayuno con Champán en la Sabana</li>
              <li>★ Traslados VIP al Aeropuerto</li>
              <li>★ Safaris Nocturnos Exclusivos</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="neon-btn">Más Popular</button>
          </div>
          <div class="price-card">
            <img src="/media/homepage/safari_luxury.jpg" alt="Safari VIP de Lujo" class="price-img" loading="lazy">
            <h3>Kilimanjaro VIP Lujo</h3>
            <p class="price-desc">La experiencia de lujo definitiva. Naturaleza salvaje combinada con confort de 5 estrellas.</p>
            <div class="price">$4,999</div>
            <ul>
              <li>👑 7 Días (Serengeti, Tarangire, Ngorongoro)</li>
              <li>👑 Vuelo Privado en Globo Aerostático</li>
              <li>👑 Alojamiento 5 Estrellas con Piscina Infinita</li>
              <li>👑 Chef Privado y Comidas Gourmet</li>
              <li>👑 Vehículo 4x4 Privado y Guía Exclusivo</li>
              <li>👑 Servicio de Conserjería VIP 24/7</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="neon-btn">Ir VIP</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section: Cerveza Safari -->
    <section class="panel beer-section-white" id="section-beer">
      <div class="beer-content-wrapper">
        <h2 class="dark-text center-text">Refresca Tu Aventura</h2>
        <div class="beer-container" id="beer-container">
          <video id="beer-video" class="native-scrub-video" src="/media/homepage/video_fondo_negro.mp4" muted playsinline preload="auto"></video>
        </div>
        <p class="dark-text center-text mt-4">Descubre el verdadero sabor de la sabana con <strong>Cerveza Safari</strong>. Mezcla africana auténtica.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 5: Conclusion -->
    <section class="panel conclusion" id="section-conclusion">
      <div class="glass-box init-anim">
        <h2 class="glow-text">Despierta África</h2>
        <p>Una nueva frontera de exploración inmersiva de la vida salvaje tanzana.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Three.js module -->
  <script>
    import('../../scripts/homepage-3d.ts');
  </script>
</HomepageLayout>
